---
title: Media Assets UI
weight: 200
group: reference
---

All media files are managed and maintained within the Content Mangager's Media Assets. Media files are stored in the folder specified during [configuration](https://www.netlifycms.org/docs/add-to-your-site/#media-and-public-folders). Uploaded files are added to content when creating Posts and Pages. 

## Managing Media Assets
Viewing, uploading, and deleting media all occur within the Media Assets section, accessed by clicking Media in the Content Manager. 

To add to the Media Library, click Upload New to select your files to add. 

To delete, select media from the library, then click Delete Selcted.

You can search through your library and display specific files by using Search.
